  "texts": [
    "As shown in Fig. 3, in order to reduce the training cost, this paper through the current hot three general-purpose model, in turn, batch text generation, image generation, image super-resolution task, the specific details are as follows.",
    "Step 1: First of all, it needs to be clear that ChatGPT is a textual dialog model and cannot generate images directly.",
    "Note that this paper uses ChatGPT 3.5, which is OPENAI's current mainstream generalized ChatGPT version (https://chat.openai.com/), without retraining.",
    "By inputting fuzzified textual descriptions of railroad scenes, ChatGPT is required to output diverse railroad environments and scenarios.",
    "The use of fuzzified descriptions introduces a level of uncertainty, allowing for the inclusion of a diverse range of scenarios."
  ]
